WEBVTT

00:00:00.316 --> 00:00:07.407
Good morning, family. I'm excited to be with you again today; I think this is the third video in a row.

00:00:07.408 --> 00:00:16.319
This video is pretty serious. The Lord has put on my heart—I'm going to tell you the things I've been praying about.

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:24.705
I've been praying over Italy and all the little tremors and the volcano.

00:00:24.706 --> 00:00:27.572
I'm going to tell you what I saw. I was caught up in the Spirit.

00:00:27.573 --> 00:00:42.078
I was just praying in the Spirit, I was worshiping, and all of a sudden I was shot up. I was looking over Italy, and Italy was so small.

00:00:42.079 --> 00:00:50.707
I was so high—I guess that's the way I want to say it—I was really, really high and I was looking down.

00:00:50.708 --> 00:00:58.747
All of a sudden, I could see a black blanket over the water over Italy.

00:00:58.748 --> 00:01:14.521
It looked like a thick cloud, but it was as black as molasses—very, very dark.

00:01:14.522 --> 00:01:36.850
It was all over the water and there were black clouds going through all the houses. It looked like a smog all around the houses.

00:01:36.851 --> 00:01:45.959
I could see the rooftops of the homes because I was up, and I could see the lights on in the houses. Angels were descending into Italy.

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:58.565
Above, the Lord pointed my attention to a massive circle, a humongous portal that was over the country of Italy.

00:01:58.566 --> 00:02:12.357
It was over where the earthquake happened last night, where I told you the volcano is at by Pompeii. There was this massive portal and there were angels in it.

00:02:12.358 --> 00:02:28.638
The angels were coming out of this massive portal, and the portal was like it was breathing—it was alive. It was swirling, and there were clouds all in it.

00:02:28.639 --> 00:02:42.045
It looked like it was opening up, and all of a sudden these angels started coming out of this massive portal—thousands of them.

00:02:42.046 --> 00:03:02.650
They were all coming down like a staircase. It was like they were all descending, but they were lined up like soldiers coming out of this massive portal over Italy.

00:03:02.651 --> 00:03:07.493
It looked like they were coming downstairs, but I could not see stairs.

00:03:07.494 --> 00:03:16.826
Through the portal, there were clouds coming out as the portal was breathing and turning. It was swirling; it was alive.

00:03:16.827 --> 00:03:36.190
The clouds coming out of the portal were humongous and beautiful—pink, blue, and purple.

00:03:36.191 --> 00:03:45.896
I believe it was Heaven. These angels were all coming down and descending onto the Earth.

00:03:45.897 --> 00:03:58.523
When they got to a certain place in the atmosphere between the portal and the Earth, they started to spread out like ants all over the place.

00:03:58.524 --> 00:04:05.639
They started scattering and they were coming even faster down onto those homes.

00:04:05.640 --> 00:04:14.998
All of a sudden, each angel was going to a place; they were on a mission, moving at the speed of light.

00:04:14.999 --> 00:04:22.861
They were moving down, and they all had beautiful robes and gowns on. It was the most amazing thing.

00:04:22.862 --> 00:04:36.008
The whole time, I'm sitting here in this chair praying in the Spirit and seeing all this, soaking it all in.

00:04:36.009 --> 00:04:50.715
I'm trying so hard to explain everything the Lord showed me in detail: the black smog.

00:04:50.716 --> 00:05:04.048
I was asking the Lord what all that black smog was. He showed me that from coast to coast, there's a lot of sex trafficking in Italy.

00:05:04.049 --> 00:05:20.457
I don't know if people don't know about it, but he was showing that there was a lot of corruption and trafficking in Italy. There was sand and things he was showing me about this.

00:05:20.458 --> 00:05:33.892
Those angels were coming down, going to these homes, and they were making a motion with their hand, like 'Come on,'telling the people to leave.

00:05:33.893 --> 00:05:57.546
It was a warning. Every angel was waving the people to come on. They did this for several minutes.

00:05:57.547 --> 00:06:05.043
In the Spirit, you couldn't really tell a time frame, but you could sense an urgency on their faces.

00:06:05.044 --> 00:06:13.799
It felt like such an urgency of a warning, telling the people to leave.

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:19.714
They didn't say anything; I could just see by their body language that they were in a hurry.

00:06:19.715 --> 00:06:30.231
All of a sudden, all of the angels stopped their arms, and I knew people were praying.

00:06:30.232 --> 00:06:41.416
I could feel the intercessory prayers from the saints, from the Christians, from people interceding for Italy in the Spirit, praying in tongues.

00:06:41.417 --> 00:07:01.739
You could feel the blanket of prayer coming out of that portal. You could feel the intercessory prayer going on.

00:07:01.740 --> 00:07:26.937
All of a sudden, all the angels froze and turned their bodies to look back up to the massive swirling light, the portal.

00:07:26.938 --> 00:07:35.635
All of a sudden, they started shooting back up into that portal, and then it was over.

00:07:35.636 --> 00:07:47.818
Then the Lord took me to another part of the vision. He said, 'I want you to focus on the canary.

00:07:47.819 --> 00:07:53.579
A canary Braden, what is the meaning of a canary in a coal mine?

00:07:53.580 --> 00:08:00.514
Study this out.'I saw a yellow canary in a cave, and there were gases.

00:08:00.515 --> 00:08:46.920
I could see a gas coming up out of the ground like a smog. The canary was swinging in a cage.

00:08:46.921 --> 00:08:49.500
I saw this birdcage in the spirit realm. I saw the canary on the little swing, swinging back and forth and chirping.

00:08:49.501 --> 00:08:49.600
All of a sudden, I looked down because I could see this mist-like gas coming up out of the ground.

00:08:49.601 --> 00:09:02.250
I took my eyes off the canary, and when I looked back, the canary was dead in the bottom of the cage—lifeless and completely gone.

00:09:02.251 --> 00:09:09.358
It happened so quickly; the gases came up and took the canary out.

00:09:09.359 --> 00:09:17.777
This is part of the vision the Lord showed me about the angels and this gas coming up out of the ground in Italy.

00:09:17.778 --> 00:09:26.939
I don't know what that was—if it was from the volcano or whatever.

00:09:26.940 --> 00:09:34.223
But I told you all I saw hundreds of thousands of people go home. I saw a massive wave coming.

00:09:34.224 --> 00:09:41.757
The Lord said, 'Pay attention to the water.'I saw the earthquakes in the water, and the people weren't paying attention.

00:09:41.758 --> 00:09:53.534
The water was what the Lord kept putting my attention to in the past visions—look at the water in the coves. He kept pointing me to that in the spirit realm.

00:09:53.535 --> 00:10:05.652
I could see with my spirit eyes what the Lord was showing me: the water in the gulf area right there by Pompeii.

00:10:05.653 --> 00:10:13.263
This is just what the Lord is showing me. I know, like I said, a major 4.4, I believe, happened last night.

00:10:13.264 --> 00:10:17.433
I saw all the rocks and the devastation, the people, and the sirens going off.

00:10:17.434 --> 00:10:42.359
There was a video my wife gave me from someone on Facebook; they were putting it on their feed there, and she was showing me, saying, 'Listen to this.'So I looked at it and I was like, 'Oh my goodness.'I guess this just happened yesterday, last night—it was our night—so not even 12 to 24 hours ago.

00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:49.966
The electric grid situation is escalating, and things are really getting intense.

00:10:49.967 --> 00:11:09.281
Okay, number two: for the past week, even from last Monday—not yesterday Monday, but the week prior—three times now the Lord has spoken to me about the electric grid in America, telling me, 'Pray over the electric grid.

00:11:09.282 --> 00:11:16.395
This is very serious.'I saw a cyberattack or it was a false flag attack.

00:11:16.396 --> 00:11:32.055
Like I said, I'm not going to just flat out say it was Russia or whoever; I'm telling you I saw something go on with our electric grid, and all of a sudden power went out in New York and major cities.

00:11:32.056 --> 00:11:38.304
It was completely dark everywhere because of what happened on this electric grid issue.

00:11:38.305 --> 00:12:01.630
And so He said, 'You're not taking this serious enough.'He warned me, saying, 'You need to pray about this more intently because of what is being planned and plotted.'I saw when the electric grid went down, for some people, it had the opportunity to be down for over three weeks.

00:12:01.631 --> 00:12:11.433
I saw the number three—for over three weeks. I saw a calendar, and I could see the days go by with people being without power.

00:12:11.434 --> 00:12:19.057
The Lord was warning me about these major cities and about this plot against America and about the power grid.

00:12:19.058 --> 00:12:26.038
Now, I don't know a timeframe or anything else about that. All I know is I'm interceding for this.

00:12:26.039 --> 00:12:34.137
This is on top of the Italy thing that He brought to my attention, warning me about it.

00:12:34.138 --> 00:12:57.539
Like I tried to tell you all about what He showed me a year ago about investing into a generator that had three fuel types—propane, gas, and natural gas—and having electricity for what was coming in the future, powering your home, finding ways to power your home through solar.

00:12:57.540 --> 00:13:06.179
They sell lights on Amazon, there's candles, there's all kinds of stuff for people to have light.

00:13:06.180 --> 00:13:19.636
I don't want to ever preach fear; I don't want to be a Debbie Downer and come on here and go wacko all the time, but I get these things from the Spirit of God, these warnings, and they're very intense.

00:13:19.637 --> 00:13:34.199
He warns me about things. For instance, I was praying over an ice storm one time, and He was telling me about Texas being without power.

00:13:34.200 --> 00:13:42.209
I kept seeing 'without power,'I kept seeing 'no heat,'I kept seeing a poisoning of the water—something was wrong with the water.

00:13:42.210 --> 00:13:59.839
I believe it was about three years now that they had a major cold front; a major arctic front came down out of the Arctic and through Canada, and really made everything really cold in Texas.

00:13:59.840 --> 00:14:14.128
They could not handle the electric load for all of the people trying to heat their homes, so the electric grid shut down because the windmills froze.

00:14:14.129 --> 00:14:23.366
All of the pipes in the houses burst because people were trying to drip their faucets, and so it shut down all of the water.

00:14:23.367 --> 00:14:28.523
They put out a warning not to drink the water because it had E.

00:14:28.524 --> 00:14:34.507
coli and all kinds of stuff, and you had to boil it before you could drink it.

00:14:34.508 --> 00:15:04.032
This lasted for quite a while, but before that happened, the Lord warned me to warn friends that lived in Texas and told them, 'You need to get at least 12 cases of water.'So I took it on myself, not knowing where it would affect me, so I went out and bought all the water too because of what I was seeing in the spirit; it was very alarming.

00:15:04.033 --> 00:15:11.357
It had nothing to do with my household; we had a lot of water to drink for a while.

00:15:11.358 --> 00:15:18.543
When you're seeing in the spirit, I always want to tell you: this does not always affect everybody.

00:15:18.544 --> 00:15:29.638
There's a lot of ground to cover from Canada to Mexico, from the Atlantic to the Pacific.

00:15:29.639 --> 00:15:40.379
Whenever I'm seeing in the spirit, I don't want to always alarm everybody and say the power's going out for all of America, because I don't believe that.

00:15:40.380 --> 00:15:54.293
I want you to be praying about this for your own household. It could be New York; like I said, I saw New York, I saw a major city, and I believe it was New York, but I don't want to assume.

00:15:54.294 --> 00:16:10.359
It could be Chicago, but I saw a lot of big buildings. So I want to warn you all to pray about the power grid with me. This is serious.

00:16:10.360 --> 00:16:22.858
Instead of going, 'Well, I'm just going to go out and buy everything off of Amazon from coast to coast,'because the power grid's not going to go down for the whole country for three weeks.

00:16:22.859 --> 00:16:30.516
I don't believe that. I believe that certain areas, just like my story about Dallas and what the Lord was showing me there.

00:16:30.517 --> 00:16:40.533
I thought, because I live in Oklahoma, that this was going to be about Oklahoma, all the power going out and the water going bad, and I'm trying to warn everybody.

00:16:40.534 --> 00:16:51.051
But I'm seeing in part, I'm hearing in part. When you're doing that, I always try to be quick to obey whenever He tells me something.

00:16:51.052 --> 00:17:04.973
This was a word for Texas, and it affected a lot of people in Texas—hundreds of thousands of people—and they were without power for two weeks or more.

00:17:04.974 --> 00:17:17.370
It was bad. No heat, and people were staying in sleeping bags and trying to keep warm with their families, and pipes were bursting everywhere; it was a mess.

00:17:17.371 --> 00:17:31.592
Like I said, I get these cues. Those are the three things: about Campi Flegrei in Italy and the electric grid.

00:17:31.593 --> 00:17:43.650
I hope this video blessed you. I try to give you things the Lord has given me in prayer and keep you all updated.

00:17:43.651 --> 00:17:55.164
Let's pray. I believe we can intercede right now for the people of Italy and for the people of America.

00:17:55.165 --> 00:18:01.739
Father, I thank You. Lord, right now in the name of Jesus, we lift up Italy.

00:18:01.740 --> 00:18:11.643
We lift up this volcano and the earthquakes taking place. You said, Lord, that perilous times would come.

00:18:11.644 --> 00:18:26.999
You warned us that there would be earthquakes in diverse places, there would be volcanoes and events that were fearful, that You said men's hearts would fail them for fear for looking after the things that were coming upon the earth.

00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:36.036
Father, I thank You that we are all awake and listening to what the Spirit of the Lord is saying.

00:18:36.037 --> 00:18:40.652
That we would hear Your voice, and a stranger's voice we would not follow.

00:18:40.653 --> 00:18:48.279
If we are in harm's way, if we are not listening to what the Spirit of the Lord said, shake us inside.

00:18:48.280 --> 00:19:09.564
Show us, Lord, what we're supposed to do for our families, that we'd hear You before danger comes, that we would know Your voice, Father, and that we would know the difference between the spirit of fear trying to torment us versus the Holy Ghost trying to warn us.

00:19:09.565 --> 00:19:15.779
That we will not be led by emotion; we would be led by the Holy Ghost.

00:19:15.780 --> 00:19:36.545
I pray for every single person watching this video, that they would learn to meditate on Your word and yield themselves to the Spirit of God and be able to hear Your voice clearly.

00:19:36.546 --> 00:19:57.239
We call clarity in their ears in the name of Jesus. With spiritual ears, we call supernatural giftings to see into the spirit realm, to know Your voice and hear warnings of danger.

00:19:57.240 --> 00:20:04.879
Father, I thank You that they would hear You right now concerning their lives.

00:20:04.880 --> 00:20:17.751
Clarity in the spirit, like tuning in a radio station to a clear channel, moving the antenna.

00:20:17.752 --> 00:20:38.095
'God, I'm going to put myself at Your feet, and I will be at the spout where the glory comes out, and I am not going to be in fear about what the devil's doing, but I have authority over the devil.'And I'm going to have wisdom concerning this, and I'm not going to be moved by what I see or what I feel.

00:20:38.096 --> 00:20:46.139
I am moved by what the word of God says, and we're going to hear your voice, Father, and we're going to do exactly what you tell us to do.

00:20:46.140 --> 00:20:53.395
Father, I thank you for that. Father, I pray protection over the people over Italy.

00:20:53.396 --> 00:20:58.151
I pray protection over the believers, Father; they will be out of harm's way.

00:20:58.152 --> 00:21:01.647
Father, I thank you that those angels are coming out of that portal.

00:21:01.648 --> 00:21:12.959
I thank you, Lord, that you give a strong warning even in the midnight hour, in dreams and visions, and things like that to protect the people from what's coming.

00:21:12.960 --> 00:21:17.943
Father, I thank you, Lord, that whether it's about the electric grid over Miami, from L.A.

00:21:17.944 --> 00:21:29.699
to Phoenix to Denver to Seattle, wherever it may be—the warnings that you're giving me right now—I thank you, Father, that this will not happen.

00:21:29.700 --> 00:21:40.572
We take authority over these cyberattacks. We take authority over false flag events, and we say in the name of Jesus, you will not do this.

00:21:40.573 --> 00:21:46.634
In the name of Jesus, we plead the blood of Jesus over our power grid.

00:21:46.635 --> 00:21:57.133
We say we will have power; it will not disrupt life or cause people to lose their life because they need the electricity to survive.

00:21:57.134 --> 00:22:01.515
I thank you, Father, that there is a covering over these people.

00:22:01.516 --> 00:22:08.168
I thank you, Lord, that we would hear your voice concerning these things, and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:22:08.169 --> 00:22:18.119
In America, I thank you, Lord, that our people would be wise on how to handle things in our NSA and the computer people.

00:22:18.120 --> 00:22:25.199
Father, I thank you, Lord, that at Homeland Security, the people would know and they would know how to protect us—the Army, the Corps of Engineers—all the people.

00:22:25.200 --> 00:22:32.636
Father, I thank you that you give wisdom, revelation, and knowledge over these people to block attacks from foreign adversaries.

00:22:32.637 --> 00:22:42.499
And if it is a false flag or whatever, Father, we ask you, God, to expose all wicked plots and plans.

00:22:42.500 --> 00:22:52.319
Expose all wicked plans in Jesus'name—uncovering, and uncovering, and uncovering in Jesus'name.

00:22:52.320 --> 00:22:58.276
We believe we receive this right now in the name of Jesus. Now, Father, I pray over their finances.

00:22:58.277 --> 00:23:14.362
Every person who sowed and believes in their covenant for a supernatural harvest concerning their finances—I pray over their finances in the name of Jesus for a hundredfold return over what they sow.

00:23:14.363 --> 00:23:22.984
I speak to their finances right now in the name of Jesus; great blessing is on their houses, great prosperity is over their home.

00:23:22.985 --> 00:23:36.003
And God, I thank you, Lord, for jobs and better jobs, raises and bonuses, settlements, interest and income, rebates and returns, checks in the mail, gifts and surprises, finding money, bills paid off, blessing, and increase.

00:23:36.004 --> 00:23:44.999
Father, I thank you, Lord, that every need they have is met and every debt is canceled in the name of Jesus.

00:23:45.000 --> 00:23:48.538
Father, I pray over their health and their bodies in wholeness and wellness.

00:23:48.539 --> 00:23:53.339
In the name of Jesus, we take authority over sickness right now.

00:23:53.340 --> 00:24:11.331
We come against the sickness and disease; we come against manifestations of cancers, diabetes, heart disease, all kinds of dementia and Alzheimer's, and like I said, PTSD and all kinds of bondage from perversions.

00:24:11.332 --> 00:24:28.503
We command it to go now in Jesus'name. From all kinds of addictions—to alcohol, to prescription medications, from drugs to all kinds of bondage—we take authority over bondage right now in the name of Jesus.

00:24:28.504 --> 00:24:37.019
Strongholds be broken off of their lives; we call bondage and strongholds to be broken by the power of the Lord.

00:24:37.020 --> 00:24:43.379
We call the blood of Jesus over this right now. We plead the blood of Jesus over this.

00:24:43.380 --> 00:24:50.295
We thank you from the North to South, the East to West; we call angels to minister to us right now in Jesus'name.

00:24:50.296 --> 00:24:56.004
We thank you, Lord. We pray over rain and an abundance of rain over our areas.

00:24:56.005 --> 00:25:00.105
We break drought in the name of Jesus. We take authority over drought.

00:25:00.106 --> 00:25:05.694
We speak to the rain; we call the rain to come from the North, the South, the East, and the West.

00:25:05.695 --> 00:25:09.853
We call low-pressure systems to come in right now in the name of Jesus.

00:25:09.854 --> 00:25:14.422
We call forth low-pressure systems and the moisture to come up.

00:25:14.423 --> 00:25:19.956
We call rain to come; we claim rain, rain, rain in Jesus'name.

00:25:19.957 --> 00:25:28.079
The former rain and the latter rain, even the spiritual rain of the Holy Ghost, rain over this nation.

00:25:28.080 --> 00:25:37.139
We call an abundance of rain to come down right now in the name of Jesus. We call your outpouring of the spirit, Lord.

00:25:37.140 --> 00:25:44.699
Bring us a great outpouring, a great outflow of a great river, a tidal wave of your presence upon this nation.

00:25:44.700 --> 00:25:52.093
We pray over the leaders, over the people who are over this country, from Joe Biden all the way down.

00:25:52.094 --> 00:25:57.864
We pray for even the smallest person that's in power; we say in the name of Jesus, they would have wisdom.

00:25:57.865 --> 00:26:11.099
Father, I thank you, Lord, they would have a fear of the Lord inside of them to make godly decisions.

00:26:11.100 --> 00:26:28.079
In closing, Father, I just thank you, Lord. I thank you for your presence, for in your presence there's fullness of joy.

00:26:28.080 --> 00:26:38.579
Lord, we rest in you today. We take the care out of our prayer, for if you're begging, you're not believing.

00:26:38.580 --> 00:26:50.099
We thank you, Lord, for where the spirit of the Lord is, there is freedom, and we will not fear.

00:26:50.100 --> 00:27:06.058
We will not fear in Jesus'name. We plead the blood over our nation. We plead the blood of Jesus over this right now.

00:27:06.059 --> 00:27:16.259
I thank you, Father, that we have eyes to see what you have to show us, ears to hear, and I plead the blood of Jesus over us right now in Jesus'name.

00:27:16.260 --> 00:27:26.264
Amen. Well, okay. I thank you all for joining me today. I really do.

00:27:26.265 --> 00:27:35.905
I hope this has blessed you all. I really appreciate you taking the time to watch my videos.

00:27:35.906 --> 00:27:44.245
It means a lot to me. I'm new at this; I'm just learning like you all every day.

00:27:44.246 --> 00:27:51.778
Every day we learn and we follow after the voice of the Lord, and he is faithful. He's faithful to us.

00:27:51.779 --> 00:27:57.156
The presence of the Lord really settled in on me right there when I was praying.

00:27:57.157 --> 00:28:12.599
I saw some things I'd have to pray about. Well, y'all put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:28:12.600 --> 00:28:17.339
Jesus loves you so much, and I'm so thankful that you watched my video today.

00:28:17.340 --> 00:28:24.161
Y'all have a blessed day and we'll see you next time. Bye-bye.

